Two T204 Ramly cards:

John Anderson Blank Back variation SGC 30, very scarce card only 3 sales on Google, one of which is the same card with a backstamp MK designation. This exact same card sold in Huggins & Scott in 2008 for $475 plus the juice. Offered today for $500 delivered. Check or Money order preferred but will take paypal "money owed"

"Wild" Bill Donovan PSA 5, solid corners, one small toned area in the center. $425 delivered, which is lower than most 5's sold in 2013 according to Card Target. Payment as above.
